    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Game</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In a dystopian future, health and safety laws are forgotten, and contestants from around the world battle it out in a new and emerging underground sport!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With quick frantic rounds and feel good gameplay, this high energy game is a must for local competitive fun with friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, with <strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong>, you can stream your game and play with up to 8 people, with no need to set up servers or wait for the perfect number of </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >players to join a room, just call up your mates and play and stream instantly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/e745caaa922718b778eb2a4071fea481.poster.avif?t=1763994920\" width=640 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/e745caaa922718b778eb2a4071fea481.webm?t=1763994920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/e745caaa922718b778eb2a4071fea481.mp4?t=1763994920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/094686f50d1879e10b8e153c77e11c96.avif?t=1763994920\" width=640 height=210 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Short brutal rounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ever moving ball</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Powerups for added chaos</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/f228c19fec65d51a330d544423b8e924.poster.avif?t=1763994920\" width=640 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/f228c19fec65d51a330d544423b8e924.webm?t=1763994920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/f228c19fec65d51a330d544423b8e924.mp4?t=1763994920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/429130599368ada1e7d5bfddf21f6270.avif?t=1763994920\" width=640 height=210 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Aim with your analogue stick for precise shots!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Curve the ball after you've hit it for added accuracy! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Freeze mid-air and ready your shot for the perfect return!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/a0377336aa5046f4c7b7f97023ba4cf6.poster.avif?t=1763994920\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/a0377336aa5046f4c7b7f97023ba4cf6.webm?t=1763994920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/a0377336aa5046f4c7b7f97023ba4cf6.mp4?t=1763994920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888270/extras/fa434c2c7145dd198ce1ca0172055526.avif?t=1763994920\" width=640 height=210 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A host of unique quirky characters to choose from!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 Different Gamemodes! (Original, Points, Marksman, &amp; Goals)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play in a team of 4v4, 3v3, 2v2 or play PvP, all against all!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Many music tracks to choose from, ranging from D&amp;B &amp; Techno, to Breakbeat &amp; House!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
